<a name="Creating Auto-Grader Type Questions">
<h4>
2.3.1.  Creating Auto-Grader Type Questions
</h4>
</a>
<p>
After the adding a question and choosing the desired type (as covered in 
<a href="question-management.html">Section 2.3</a>), the screen will change accordingly 
depending on the chosen question type.

<p> 
This section covers questions that can be auto-graded, such as True/False and Multiple Choice 
questions. 

<p>
---True/False---

<p>
Choosing <tt>True/False</tt> as the question type loads the following screen as shown in Figure 3-9.

<br>
<br>
<hr>
