<p align=center>
<img src="images/true-false.png">
</p>
<p align=center> Figure 3-9: True/False Question </p>
<hr>
</a>
<br>

<p>
<tt>Question</tt>, <tt>Coures</tt>, <tt>Points</tt>, <tt>Subject</tt>, and <tt>Difficulty</tt> are discussed
in <a href="question-management.html">Section 2.3</a>.

<p>
In a True/False Question, <tt>Answer</tt> is a drop-down menu. When the user clicks on it, 
there is only 2 choices: True, False.

